Kluster's eyes widen as he sees a boulder heading for Rex, who was near 
Tankorr.

"Rex, watch out!" he yells, Rex barely sidestepping in time.

"Just use old-fashioned guns!" Kluster yells at Hot Rod, firing at Tankorr.
